FBIS3-24842 "drafr022_c_94011" FBIS-AFR-94-022 Document Type:Daily Report 2 Feb 1994 REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA Blast Reported at Union Offices in Western Transvaal MB0202064794 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in English 0600 GMT 2 Feb 94 MB0202064794 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] An explosion has rocked the offices of the National Union of Mineworkers and the National Union of Metalworkers of South Africa at Klerksdorp in the Western Transvaal. The blast was reported earlier this morning and is believed to have caused extensive damage. No further details are known at this stage.
